commit.message: Pass the complete set of args to AC_INIT.
Remove unnecessary localization of h2o::internals namespace.
Use assertions instead of exceptions for invalid uses.
Add a initialized() method to check for 'uninitialized' state.
automake: add a rule for NEWS file.
Document the API in header file.
expand(): throw std::range_error in R5 instead of runtime_error.
expand(): don't fail explicitly in R1, clean up.
Move test executables to tests/ subdir.
Use a complete class for Region enum.
Use class storage rather than global variables.
Update remaining check functions to use constructors.
Add a convenience h2o::H2O::pT() static constr.
Region 3: add tests for remaining subregions.
